symbol of future market data

Source: R/md_future.R
md_future_symbol.Rd

md_future_symbol search the symbols in future market indicators that provided by sina finance only currently.

md_future_symbol()

Examples

# \donttest{
# interactivly search future market symbols
sybs = md_future_symbol()
